Author: sucks_tosuck
Text: I feel you on this one ughh my cousin is losing weight and she and her mother (my aunt) are boasting about her "success" and it's.so.triggering  Please pay attention to yourself, try to not think about it much even though it's hard ... And yeah losing weight won't make you happy, in fact attempting it will make you moody and tired; please stay safe, it's a dark place...
